dictionary.name: _code
dictionary.string: "//this shader only works properly with premultiplied alpha blend mode&#000a;uniform float aura_width=2.0;&#000a;uniform color aura_color=vec4(0.4,0.7,0.3,1);&#000a;uniform color modulate=color(0.2,0.4,1.0,1.0);&#000a;&#000a;vec4 col = vec4(modulate.rgb,tex(TEXTURE,UV).a*modulate.a);&#000a;vec2 ps = TEXTURE_PIXEL_SIZE;&#000a;float a;&#000a;float maxa=col.a;&#000a;float mina=col.a;&#000a;a=tex(TEXTURE,UV+vec2(0,-aura_width)*ps).a;&#000a;maxa=max(a,maxa); &#000a;mina=min(a,mina);&#000a;a=tex(TEXTURE,UV+vec2(0,aura_width)*ps).a;&#000a;maxa=max(a,maxa); &#000a;mina=min(a,mina);&#000a;a=tex(TEXTURE,UV+vec2(-aura_width,0)*ps).a;&#000a;maxa=max(a,maxa); &#000a;mina=min(a,mina);&#000a;a=tex(TEXTURE,UV+vec2(aura_width,0)*ps).a;&#000a;maxa=max(a,maxa); &#000a;mina=min(a,mina);&#000a;col.rgb*=col.a;&#000a;COLOR=col;//mix(col,aura_color,maxa-mina);&#000a;&#000a;float auraa=(maxa-mina);&#000a;&#000a;COLOR.rgb+=aura_color.rgb*(maxa-mina);"
